{"tid":2012140,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【國際線】英國國會反華小組成立開 twitter，大家訂閱咗未?","createTime":"2020-05-11T12:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T09:26:11.000Z","uid":305299,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6e014587df554f05882097bd7e24912857bdffe0","tid":2012140,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MzxR7KP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMzxR7KP.png&h=df91457c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個名雖然叫中國研究小組，好似好中性，而啲選圖更加好似係親中忝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但如果有留意開英國新聞嘅朋友，就會知道有一個類似好中性嘅物體叫歐洲研究小組 (European Research Group)，但一個咁中性嘅小組，就偏偏係搞到英國脫歐嘅主力推手之一，為脫歐出謀獻策<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國國會議員依家另外成立依個小組，故意改一個類似嘅名，就明顯話畀全世界知，佢地唔係中國友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家再睇睇佢地啲 tweets 就知道佢地真係唔係同中國friend 底，而且佢地亦都同時有關注香港嘅事態發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明白大家對英國嘅期望唔高，甚至可以話係負數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以依個小組4月底成立以來，香港都唔多人理，睇佢地就連有關香港嘅 tweets都無咩人畀心心同留言就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但正正喺一向普遍親中嘅英國政壇入面，依一批國會保守黨議員願意做出頭鳥，帶頭成立依個反華小組，亦都唔係容易嘅事，係一個好難得嘅開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且有撐港議員 Tom Tugendhat 做組長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，希望大家可以抽少少時間去下面個傳送門 follow 佢地個 twitter，畀啲支持佢地<br />\n亦都當然希望佢地可以好似歐洲研究小組咁，最終推動到英中關係分道揚鑣 (decouple) 喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yW5kgDm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyW5kgDm.png&h=1c3769ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZQ4Jin.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZQ4Jin.png&h=22a6fb98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTtYNK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTtYNK2.png&h=ac13af05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n= = = = =<br />\ntwitter 傳送門：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ChinaResearchGp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChinaResearchGp&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=7dbfa382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ChinaResearchGp</a><br />\nBBC 新聞報導：<br />\nCoronavirus: Tory MPs to examine 'rise of China'<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-52414635\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-52414635&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=e8c451e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-52414635&h=dcea3fd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-52414635</a>"},{"pid":"ead45c9dc64928edb0c36fded5bd14200d330087","tid":2012140,"uid":283977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"撐"},{"pid":"67560522e1c2e468bc55ff5a4ce43551368d381c","tid":2012140,"uid":91721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:53:24.000Z","msg":"仲要係Tom Tugenhat揸旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907977e9d46d8ecd5beb6ddcdb9845a37efad4bf","tid":2012140,"uid":222925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59dae105f74f6a22174f2b220daf7ff1cc1d244","tid":2012140,"uid":213037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\