10:03.000Z","msg":"P 牌推"},{"pid":"6d3d54195ee04b5dc4404cf323e51b63a1061b3b","tid":2012140,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T01:11:43.000Z","msg":"我依類我親華反共<br />\n加唔加佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527f0c2cbf7edf4fbed2c096e78b689d21d95682","tid":2012140,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"晨早FOLLOW咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce9ee1812b7b66abe02740101a82336eb2e4aa1","tid":2012140,"uid":213037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:23:16.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線手足整咗個網站出嚟比大家做task<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後大家無藉口唔打國際線喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲bookmark 佢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Ftwitter&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=430ed191\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/twitter</a><br />\n<br />\n入bot 拎任務24小時更新：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=c086b746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n另有手足會係佢Twitter Account 每日更新任務:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTweetingforHK&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=9df52f0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK</a><br />\n<br />\n或者download 香城online 個app 都有Twitter 任務做<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKOnlinePortal&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=ad3dd544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal</a><br />\n<br />\nLike retweet reply<br />\nTask2係國際戰線，唔好淨係推Task 1,Task2都好重要。<br />\n*如果見到想用嘅圖已經有手足用咗請搵第二張圖<br />\n*如果見到已經有好多圖就唔好再放圖，只留文字（短短地都得）<br />\n*唔好只係扔低張圖咩字都唔打<br />\n*唔知留咩好就like 手足留言或者啲對我哋有利嘅留言<br />\n<br />\n將Twitter 變成日常，每人每日做少少。<br />\n每人嘅一小步加埋就係一大步。<br />\n我哋唔知做咩先有用，所以咩都試下咩都做下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be0c62670d01fb74b234bdcc35a9df42a6fd1e0","tid":2012140,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4bf10ffb94252d84a1d60689633f7a0730fb8d2","tid":2012140,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:26:11.000Z","msg":"推"}]}